						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hold&nbsp;on</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">in&nbsp;the&nbsp;image...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>If you look closely, Reynolds has a scar on the right side in 2012, but on the left before he's taken into protective custody.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>That and Department of multidimensional imbrication suggests one thing, but there's something else I wanna ask : Do hume levels fluctuate in their nerve systems <em>only</em>?</p> 
