				<pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2019 17:15:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Crashington</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5028224</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong>Thoughts:</strong></p> <p>My first real attempt at dialogue and actual emotional writing, that is not just describing emotional events. I very much hope you like it!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hide!</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>This is intended to be pretty vague, so I hope you can come to your own conclusion you are satisfied with. A few people during the crit process have learned my intention, but I will not spoil it here. Look closely at the images though, if you have not noticed.</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p><strong>More by this author:</strong></p> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/poi-3181-198-file">http://www.scp-wiki.net/poi-3181-198-file</a></p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Critique&nbsp;Credit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><strong>Critique Credit:</strong></p> <p>Big thanks to: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574789563" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2104082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574789563" alt="ManyMeats" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2104082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" >ManyMeats</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574789563" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fortunefavorsbold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1552358&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574789563" alt="FortuneFavorsBold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1552358)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fortunefavorsbold" >FortuneFavorsBold</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4176498&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574789563" alt="Nameless Mediocre" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4176498)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" >Nameless Mediocre</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574789563" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>.<br /> Biggest of thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www